Saturday 2nd August 2014. That is when, as part of the BBC Radio 1 Weekend in Ibiza, Cream will host a special one-off show at Privilege Ibiza. Grandiose compilation for the 20th anniversary of the famous party series "Cream" at Amnesia in Ibiza. The definitive Ibiza compilation of the year with 3 CDs full of dance floor anthems of Deep House, Trance / Progressive and EDM. From Avicii and Armin van Buuren on Clean Bandit and Disclosure to Calvin Harris and Deadmau5!
